<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 16:08:42 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>最新民意调查显示，大多数以色列人表示加沙不太可能取得“绝对胜利”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/most-israelis-say-absolute-victory-in-gaza-unlikely-according-to-new-poll/0000018d-cc0e-d6e9-a38d-fc1fe3ab0000</link><description>“绝对胜利”这个词是故意选择的，因为它已成为本杰明·内塔尼亚胡总理在新闻发布会和外语采访中喜欢用的词，尽管他不愿定义其实际含义</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 15:48:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/most-israelis-say-absolute-victory-in-gaza-unlikely-according-to-new-poll/0000018d-cc0e-d6e9-a38d-fc1fe3ab0000</guid></item><item><title>哈佛亲巴勒斯坦教职人员团体为分享带有反犹太主义图像的帖子而道歉</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/harvard-pro-palestinian-faculty-group-apologizes-for-sharing-post-with-antisemitic-image/0000018d-cc0e-d6e9-a38d-fc1f836d0000</link><description>哈佛大学谴责了这张照片，并表示其管理委员会将从现在开始审查这些帖子。该大学写道：“我们以最强烈的措辞谴责这些帖子”</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 15:31:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/harvard-pro-palestinian-faculty-group-apologizes-for-sharing-post-with-antisemitic-image/0000018d-cc0e-d6e9-a38d-fc1f836d0000</guid></item><item><title>美国称联合国最高法院不应敦促以色列立即从巴勒斯坦声称拥有主权的土地上撤军</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/un-top-court-shouldnt-urge-israel-to-immediately-withdraw-from-palestinian-claimed-lands/0000018d-cbd1-dd47-adfd-dbf528560000</link><description>在国际法院就以色列占领领土举行听证会的第三天，美国代表告诉专家组不要试图“通过针对仅关注某一方行为的问题的咨询意见”来解决以色列-巴勒斯坦冲突</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 15:05:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/un-top-court-shouldnt-urge-israel-to-immediately-withdraw-from-palestinian-claimed-lands/0000018d-cbd1-dd47-adfd-dbf528560000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军高级律师：一些士兵在加沙的行为已经“跨越了犯罪门槛”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/top-idf-lawyer-some-israeli-soldiers-have-engaged-in-criminal-behavior-during-war/0000018d-cbb5-d6e9-a38d-fbbdc0610000</link><description>在给以色列国防军指挥官的一封信中，军法署署长指出，必须对那些“跨越犯罪门槛”的士兵采取行动，例如“在行动上不合理地使用武力、抢劫、掠夺私人财产和破坏平民财产”</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 14:40:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/top-idf-lawyer-some-israeli-soldiers-have-engaged-in-criminal-behavior-during-war/0000018d-cbb5-d6e9-a38d-fbbdc0610000</guid></item><item><title>撰写太空道德准则的以色列豪猪专家</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/science-and-health/2024-02-21/ty-article-magazine/the-israeli-porcupine-expert-who-wrote-the-ethics-code-for-space/0000018d-c6d5-d234-a9ff-eeffcb3d0000</link><description>兹维·塞弗教授曾踏遍非洲森林，为内塔尼亚胡封锁的天才和才华撰写法案，与比尔·盖茨和安吉拉·默克尔交流思想，并研究伊朗人。因此，难怪他将自己的道德准则带到了联合国</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 14:05:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/science-and-health/2024-02-21/ty-article-magazine/the-israeli-porcupine-expert-who-wrote-the-ethics-code-for-space/0000018d-c6d5-d234-a9ff-eeffcb3d0000</guid></item><item><title>承认巴勒斯坦国是对恐怖活动的奖励吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/why-recognizing-a-palestinian-state-is-not-a-reward-for-terror/0000018d-cb0e-ddae-a18f-ffbecc420000</link><description>以色列总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡对人类的复杂性和历史的进程一无所知，希望让世界相信巴勒斯坦国只不过是“恐怖的奖励”</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 12:00:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/why-recognizing-a-palestinian-state-is-not-a-reward-for-terror/0000018d-cb0e-ddae-a18f-ffbecc420000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵在加沙北部战斗中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldier-killed-in-northern-gaza-fighting/0000018d-cae7-ddae-a18f-ffff50f80000</link><description>21 岁的亚伯拉罕·沃瓦根上士在纳哈尔旅服役。沃加文 (Wogaven) 是内坦亚居民，身后留下父母和 11 名兄弟姐妹</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 11:30:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldier-killed-in-northern-gaza-fighting/0000018d-cae7-ddae-a18f-ffff50f80000</guid></item><item><title>以色列新报告称，哈马斯 10 月 7 日期间及之后的性暴力是“系统性和蓄意的”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/hamas-sexual-violence-systematic-and-deliberate-new-israeli-report-says/0000018d-cad6-d09f-a3df-eaf609c30000</link><description>以色列强奸危机中心协会发布了一份基于证词、采访和其他来源的报告，表明哈马斯的性暴力是一项“涉及系统性、有针对性的性虐待的明确行动策略”</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 11:04:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/hamas-sexual-violence-systematic-and-deliberate-new-israeli-report-says/0000018d-cad6-d09f-a3df-eaf609c30000</guid></item><item><title>无人机的黄金：大规模泄漏揭示了伊朗在俄罗斯的沙希德项目</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-02-21/ty-article-magazine/gold-for-drones-massive-leak-reveals-the-iranian-shahed-project-in-russia/0000018d-bb85-dd5e-a59d-ffb729890000</link><description>文件揭示了售价 20 万美元的 Shahed 136 如何成为俄罗斯在乌克兰武库中的致命武器，以及先进型号的外观</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 10:51:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-02-21/ty-article-magazine/gold-for-drones-massive-leak-reveals-the-iranian-shahed-project-in-russia/0000018d-bb85-dd5e-a59d-ffb729890000</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦真的“代表巴勒斯坦”吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article-magazine/.premium/does-pakistan-really-stand-for-palestine/0000018d-cb11-d09f-a3df-ebb500570000</link><description>从文学节到政治神职人员，加沙战争加剧了巴基斯坦对以色列本已过度的敌意。虽然宣扬美德的进步人士和反犹太主义伊斯兰主义者在庆祝哈马斯方面找到了共同点，但他们真正在做什么来拯救巴勒斯坦人的生命？</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 10:42:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article-magazine/.premium/does-pakistan-really-stand-for-palestine/0000018d-cb11-d09f-a3df-ebb500570000</guid></item><item><title>巴西总统用几句话抹去了他与以色列和犹太复国主义的所有热情联系</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/in-a-few-sentences-brazils-president-erased-all-his-warm-connections-with-israel/0000018d-caab-d7bf-a19d-eebf5c530000</link><description>作为以色列的长期朋友和支持者，卢拉总统将以色列在加沙的行动与纳粹针对犹太人的行动进行了比较，这让总统与以色列之间数十年的善意化为泡影。</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 10:36:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/in-a-few-sentences-brazils-president-erased-all-his-warm-connections-with-israel/0000018d-caab-d7bf-a19d-eebf5c530000</guid></item><item><title>叙利亚称以色列空袭大马士革居民区，造成两人死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/syria-says-israeli-strikes-hit-damascus-residential-area-killing-two/0000018d-caf0-d09f-a3df-eaf498230000</link><description>以色列尚未证实袭击事件，但叙利亚人权组织负责人表示，袭击事件与上个月在贝鲁特发生的哈马斯高级官员被暗杀事件类似</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 10:03:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/syria-says-israeli-strikes-hit-damascus-residential-area-killing-two/0000018d-caf0-d09f-a3df-eaf498230000</guid></item><item><title>耶路撒冷第二圣殿的奇怪石盒被发现。这是犹太洁食吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-02-21/ty-article/strange-stone-box-from-second-temple-jerusalem-is-revealed-was-it-kosher/0000018d-cad5-ddae-a18f-ffff2aa30000</link><description>这个盒子由石灰石制成，就像古代犹太家庭典型的石质厨具一样，盒子上有炭化痕迹——这是 2000 年前耶路撒冷被罗马人摧毁的痕迹</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 09:09:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-02-21/ty-article/strange-stone-box-from-second-temple-jerusalem-is-revealed-was-it-kosher/0000018d-cad5-ddae-a18f-ffff2aa30000</guid></item><item><title>对于内塔尼亚胡来说，停滞是完美的环境。对于以色列来说，这意味着灾难</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/for-netanyahu-stagnation-is-the-perfect-environment-for-israel-it-spells-disaster/0000018d-c88b-ddae-a18f-ffbf6c030000</link><description>尽管上周反对党因政府试图将卡西夫逐出议会而陷入内讧，但联盟成员的信心却在不断增强。尽管艾森科特比甘茨更激进，但他们都陷入了同一个陷阱</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 04:06:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/for-netanyahu-stagnation-is-the-perfect-environment-for-israel-it-spells-disaster/0000018d-c88b-ddae-a18f-ffbf6c030000</guid></item><item><title>在美国加大努力斡旋人质释放协议后，以色列持谨慎乐观态度</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/israel-cautiously-optimistic-after-u-s-ramps-up-efforts-to-broker-a-hostage-release-deal/0000018d-c82a-ddae-a18f-ffbea2f30000</link><description>几周以来，耶路撒冷首次出现了一些乐观情绪，认为美国谈判另一项协议的努力将取得成果。会谈目前集中在几个关键问题上，主要是以色列将释放的人质与巴勒斯坦囚犯的比例以及停火将持续多久</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 04:02:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/israel-cautiously-optimistic-after-u-s-ramps-up-efforts-to-broker-a-hostage-release-deal/0000018d-c82a-ddae-a18f-ffbea2f30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列和黎巴嫩边境拉响火箭警报</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article-live/qatar-says-medicine-delivered-to-hostages-u-s-vetoes-un-resolution-demanding-cease-fire/0000018d-c9ac-d09f-a3df-e9bcee6d0000</link><description>叙利亚报道以色列袭击大马士革住宅区 ■ 伊朗指责以色列破坏天然气管道 ■ 据报道以色列袭击加沙车辆造成人员伤亡 ■ 以色列国防军高级律师表示，有士兵参与战争犯罪行为 ■ 以色列士兵在加沙战斗中丧生</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 03:36:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article-live/qatar-says-medicine-delivered-to-hostages-u-s-vetoes-un-resolution-demanding-cease-fire/0000018d-c9ac-d09f-a3df-e9bcee6d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列总检察长警告内塔尼亚胡政府：不要使用执法手段镇压抗议活动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/israeli-ag-warns-netanyahus-government-dont-use-law-enforcement-to-quash-protests/0000018d-c896-d09f-a3df-e8b6c4e70000</link><description>加利·巴哈拉夫-米亚拉要求高等法院驳回内盖夫发展部长对她和州检察官提起的诉讼，试图迫使他们起诉反司法改革抗议者</description><pubDate>Tue, 20 Feb 2024 22:25:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/israeli-ag-warns-netanyahus-government-dont-use-law-enforcement-to-quash-protests/0000018d-c896-d09f-a3df-e8b6c4e70000</guid></item><item><title>亲以色列的福音派资金帮助特朗普最新的总统竞选提供资金</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-pro-israel-evangelical-money-helping-bankroll-trumps-latest-presidential-run/0000018d-c673-d207-a9dd-ff7b61290000</link><description>德克萨斯州福音派石油公司高管蒂姆·邓恩是唐纳德·特朗普竞选活动近期最引人注目的捐助者之一。与他一起的还有一些熟悉的亲以色列犹太商人，他们没有被特朗普对共和党的孤立主义压制吓倒</description><pubDate>Tue, 20 Feb 2024 20:30:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-pro-israel-evangelical-money-helping-bankroll-trumps-latest-presidential-run/0000018d-c673-d207-a9dd-ff7b61290000</guid></item><item><title>以色列财政部长称遣返加沙人质“不是最重要的事情”，引发愤怒</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-20/ty-article/.premium/finance-minister-sparks-outrage-after-saying-returning-hostages-not-most-important-thing/0000018d-c7f2-d00f-a1df-dff6849c0000</link><description>在特拉维夫国防部门前的言论之后的一场自发示威中，一名被囚禁的 18 岁青少年的父亲对斯莫特里奇说道：“如果有人认为人质不重要，那就让他们绑架你的孩子吧。”孩子们，然后你们就可以说话了”</description><pubDate>Tue, 20 Feb 2024 19:29:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-20/ty-article/.premium/finance-minister-sparks-outrage-after-saying-returning-hostages-not-most-important-thing/0000018d-c7f2-d00f-a1df-dff6849c0000</guid></item><item><title>为什么伯尼·桑德斯和 AOC 不会指责以色列在加沙实施种族灭绝</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-02-20/ty-article/.highlight/why-bernie-sanders-aoc-wont-accuse-israel-of-genocide-in-gaza/0000018d-c762-d00f-a1df-